Package: scatr
Type: Package
Title: Create Scatter Plots with Marginal Density or Box Plots
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2017-12-05
Author: Ravi Selker
Maintainer: Ravi Selker <selker.ravi@gmail.com>
Description: Allows you to make clean, good-looking scatter plots with the option to 
    easily add marginal density or box plots on the axes. It is also available as a module for 'jamovi'
    (see <https://www.jamovi.org> for more information). 'Scatr' is based on the 
    'cowplot' package by Claus O. Wilke and the 'ggplot2' package by Hadley Wickham.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2)
Imports: 
    jmvcore (>= 0.8.0),
    R6, 
    ggplot2, 
    cowplot, 
    ggstance, 
    ggridges,
    lazyeval
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
URL: https://github.com/raviselker/scatr
BugReports: https://github.com/raviselker/scatr/issues
